---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Licensing"
  description="Free music for your podcasts, videos, games, and creative projects under Creative Commons licensing"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-8">
          Use My Music - Free & Legal
        </h1>

        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 text-center mb-12 italic">
          All my music is released under Creative Commons licensing, making it
          free to use in your podcasts, videos, games, films, and other creative
          projects.
        </p>

        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none space-y-2">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">How to Use</h2>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                Download music from <a
                  href="https://freemusicarchive.org/music/Brylie_Christopher_Oxley/"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  >Free Music Archive</a
                >, <a
                  href="https://brylie.bandcamp.com"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  >Bandcamp</a
                >, or <a
                  href="https://soundcloud.com/brylie"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  >SoundCloud</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>Use in your project (podcasts, videos, games, etc.)</li>
              <li>
                Credit with simple attribution: "Music by Brylie Christopher
                (brylie.music)"
              </li>
            </ol>
            <p class="mt-4 font-semibold">
              That's it! No permission needed, no licensing fees, no hassles.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What's Included</h2>
            <p class="font-semibold mb-2">You can:</p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mb-4">
              <li>‚úì Use in podcasts and radio shows</li>
              <li>‚úì Use in YouTube videos and films</li>
              <li>‚úì Use in video games and interactive media</li>
              <li>‚úì Use in commercial projects</li>
              <li>‚úì Modify and adapt the music</li>
              <li>‚úì Use for personal or professional projects</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="font-semibold mb-2">Please remember to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide credit/attribution</li>
              <li>Link to this website or the original track</li>
              <li>Indicate if you modified the music</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
              Featured Placements
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4">My music has been featured in:</p>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Podcasts</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.globaljustice.org.uk/the-global-justice-now-podcast/"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  ><strong>The Global Justice Now Podcast</strong></a
                > - Episodes 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11
                <br />
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm"
                  >Social justice and global issues podcast</span
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://heritageradionetwork.org/episode/from-the-pantry-rice-revelations-ep-3/"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  ><strong>Heritage Radio Network</strong></a
                > - "From the Pantry: Rice Revelations" Episode 3
                <br />
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm"
                  >Food and culture content</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Video Games</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://pipmakesgames.itch.io/controll"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  ><strong>Controll</strong></a
                > by Pip (Agapios Kokkos), cRossGameDev, BeeTeeGames
                <br />
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Available on itch.io</span>
              </li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Film & Video</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.youtube.com/@CemeteryRidgeFilms"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  ><strong>Cemetery Ridge Films</strong></a
                > - YouTube documentary series (2021-2022)
                <br />
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm"
                  >Visual documentaries of cemeteries and nature</span
