              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vzriXRYmvh0"
                  target="_blank"
                  class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline"
                  ><strong>Rural Adventurer</strong></a
                > - "The South Dakota Sojourn" (2023)
                <br />
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm"
                  >Exploration of abandoned places and prairie landscapes</span
                >
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Perfect For</h2>
