          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Questions?</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li>
                <strong>Want to use my music?</strong> Just download and use it! No
                need to ask permission.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Need something custom?</strong>
                <a
