              </li>
              <li>
                My music reaches more people who might find healing or
                connection through it
              </li>
              <li>I support a culture of openness and sharing</li>
              <li>
                Listeners can support me directly if they choose (Bandcamp)
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
